    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR5c0057-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T01:22:40.607+09:00">道可知而可行，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T01:22:44.964+09:00">但非恒久不变之道；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T01:22:54.12+09:00">名可以据实而定，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T01:22:58.514+09:00">但非恒久不 变之名。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T01:23:07.642+09:00">无名.是万物的原始；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T01:23:12.272+09:00">有名.是万物的开端。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T01:24:19.528+09:00">所以，经常保持清将无欲，可以体察其中的奥妙;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T01:24:28.444+09:00">经常保持有欲追求.可以知晓道的功用。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T01:24:42.067+09:00">这两者，同一出处而名称不同.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T01:24:49.652+09:00">都十分深远玄妙，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T01:24:54.241+09:00">玄妙而又玄妙啊.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T01:24:55.208+09:00">这是 解开所有奥妙的门径。</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
